<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Product</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
</head>
<body>
    
    <!-- 

    This file renders the product details page for the web shop.

    Structure:
    - A container div that holds the entire content.
    - A row div that contains the main content.
    - A column div that centers the product title.
    - A column div that contains the product card.

    Product Card:
    - An image of the product.
    - The product title.
    - The product description.
    - The product price.
    - A button to navigate back to the products list.

    Variables:
    - product.image: URL of the product image.
    - product.name: Name of the product (used for the alt attribute of the image).
    - product.title: Title of the product.
    - product.description: Description of the product.
    - product.price: Price of the product.
    -->
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-12">
                <h1 class="text-center">Product</h1>
            </div>

            <div class="col-12">
                <div class="card">
                    <img src="<%= product.image %>" class="card-img-top" alt="<%= product.name %>">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title
                        "><%= product.title %></h5>
                        <p class="card-text"><%= product.description %></p>
                        <p class="card-text"><strong>Hind: </strong><%= product.price %></p>
                        <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">Back to Products</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>